Jenkins : 

Jenkins is deployed based on Java Langauage 
we can automate teh build and deployment process 

Pre-reqrusiste 

1. Java should be installed in your machine
2. Jenkins Will run default port 8080 

How to install the jenkins: 
1. Lanuch a EC2 instance 

2. Add this repo 
sudo wget -O /etc/yum.repos.d/jenkins.repo \
    https://pkg.jenkins.io/redhat-stable/jenkins.repo
3. import the key  

    sudo rpm --import https://pkg.jenkins.io/redhat-stable/jenkins.io-2023.key

4. sudo yum upgrade 
5. sudo yum install jenkins 

To install java use 
sudo yum install java-21-amazon-corretto -y
cat /var/lib/jenkins/secrets/initialAdminPassword

